title: Video Alert! Varun Dhawan’s Girlfriend Natasha Dalal At Shahid Kapoor’s Party
text: Bollywood Varun Dhawan was spotted with his girlfriend Natasha Dalal at Shahid Kapoor’s pre-birthday bash. The couple walked hand-in-hand while entering the party, but avoided media photographers and didn’t pose for the shutterbugs. Watch the entire footage right here: Varun is currently gearing up for the release of Badrinath Ki Dulhania , which is set to hit the screens on 10th March.
